Return the number of times that the string "hi" appears anywhere in the given string.


countHi("abc hi ho") → 1
countHi("ABChi hi") → 2
countHi("hihi") → 2

public int countHi(String str) {
  int count = 0;
  
  for(int i = 1; i < str.length(); i++){
    if(str.substring(i-1, i+1).equals("hi")) count++;
  }
  
  return count;
}

Return the number of times that the string "hi" appears anywhere in the given string.


countHi("abc hi ho") → 1
countHi("ABChi hi") → 2
countHi("hihi") → 2
